  "body": "In terms of the UI I think we should have 2 tables:\r\n\r\n- The explicitly set config at the top\r\n- An alphabetically ordered table down the bottom that also include the values from the top table (double ups are fine).\r\n\r\nThe second table should be expandable by level, with an expand all button, so you can expand it out to what we have today, or just click to expand the bits you are interested in. \r\n\r\nIf we could make that change combined with the changes in this PR I think the editor will be way way more usable.\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @stuartwdouglas in https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/21874#issuecomment-985168266_",
